---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>The AI tool stack for solopreneurs.</h1>
			<p style="font-size: 1.2em; margin: 1.5em 0;">
				There are <strong>thousands of AI tools</strong> launching every month.
				Most are noise. A few are genuinely useful for solo founders, freelancers,
				and indie operators trying to run a business by themselves.
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Toolbase is the honest filter.</strong> We test, compare, and review the
				AI tools that actually save time and make money for one-person businesses
				— no fluff, no paid placements, no "10 ways AI will change your life" listicles.
			</p>
			<h2 style="margin-top: 2em;">What we cover</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Comparison guides:</strong> "Jasper vs Copy.ai vs ChatGPT for freelance writers" — the kind of head-to-head that saves you hours of evaluation</li>
				<li><strong>Tool-stack tutorials:</strong> "How I built a $5k/month freelance ops system using Notion AI + ClickUp + Loom"</li>
				<li><strong>Honest reviews:</strong> What works, what doesn't, what the marketing pages don't tell you</li>
				<li><strong>Free tools:</strong> Small, fast utilities we build ourselves — calculators and generators that run in your browser, no sign-up</li>
			</ul>

			<div style="border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:12px;padding:1.25em 1.5em;margin:2em 0;">
				<p style="margin:0 0 0.5em;font-size:0.75em;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;color:var(--accent);">New tool</p>
				<p style="margin:0 0 0.5em;font-size:1.3em;font-weight:700;"><a href="/tools/freelance-rate-calculator/" style="text-decoration:none;">Freelance Hourly Rate Calculator →</a></p>
				<p style="margin:0;">Work out exactly what to charge per hour — after expenses, taxes, time off, and the hours you can actually bill. Free, instant. <a href="/tools/">See all tools</a>.</p>
			</div>

			<p style="margin-top: 2em;">
				New tools and articles every week. Browse the <a href="/tools/">tools</a>, read the
				<a href="/blog">blog</a>, or check the <a href="/about">about page</a> to learn who's behind this.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
